snippet.title: Football Manager 2024 Mobile | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
You're the boss of an elite soccer team. Build a dream squad of real-life stars or coach new talent and lead them to victory in this management game.

Football Manager 2024 Mobile. Available exclusively on Netflix: www.netflix.com/game/81629644
